{"tid":2410310,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被記者問到會否接種科興疫苗 許樹昌：私人問題唔答，不應該將問題政治化","createTime":"2021-02-16T13:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T23:38:11.000Z","uid":5195,"like":9,"dislike":117,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"82d979332bc3f370e2331009ca37c6e27d781e92","tid":2410310,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T13:19:55.000Z","msg":"疫苗顧問專家委員會今日開會，會後召集人劉澤星稱，委員會一致認為中國科興疫苗的效益，比可能涉及的風險高，因此決定推薦食物及衞生局使用。<br />\n<br />\n被記者問到會否親自接種科興疫苗，以增強市民的信心，劉澤星無正面回應，僅稱「邊一隻（疫苗）到，就打邊一隻。」另一委員會成員許樹昌則以「私人問題」為由拒絕回答，並指不應該將問題政治化。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaabc6e476024fda3db8c26c99e4c37101ed9155","tid":2410310,"uid":64345,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T13:21:51.000Z","msg":"劉澤星無正面回應，僅稱「邊一隻（疫苗）到<del><span class=\"x-small\">我手</span></del>，就打邊一隻。」"},{"pid":"c69b2a8159f02274ffb7877fb71514509fcc7a2f","tid":2410310,"uid":136797,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T13:25:30.000Z","msg":"幾時問完廢勇"},{"pid":"14cd3b8efd3521392e4772e694df207959bcb765","tid":2410310,"uid":43173,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T13:41:29.000Z","msg":"蘿友坐呢個位仲點會係私人問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你打唔打都已經係公眾須知問題"},{"pid":"17d2aac582b925b34a9c84261634019fd03433c4","tid":2410310,"uid":41087,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T15:57:05.000Z","msg":"即係唔會接種<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67e6b3aa4967590b40f2386b97c50f757d0c5e3","tid":2410310,"uid":90601,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"c